description: Sunbites Cheddar & Chives Snack Crackers with Quinoa are high in wholegrain and no artificial flavours.Sunbites Cheddar & Chives Snack Crackers With Quinoa are high in wholegrains and have no artificial flavours.How do we make these bite sized crunchy wholegrain snacks, you ask?  It's simple-we take Australian corn, wheat, rice and oats and the goodness of Quinoa. We cook our crackers until they're deliciously crispy and then we sprinkle them with our scrumptious seasonings. These marvellous little crackers pop with a crisp in the mouth, which leave the flavour they harness getting your taste-buds tingling. And more good news! Our Sunbites Cheddar & Chives snack crackers are:- High in wholegrain.- Made with Quinoa.- Made with no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.- Perfect snack when you're on the go!Sunbites snacks you can feel good about.High in wholegrainsNo artificial coloursNo artificial flavoursMade with Quinoa
